_sText:
A relatively small map for anyone who likes elimination. ...and concrete.

==============
Installing:
==============
Extract to your css folder.
C:\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\username\counter-strikesource\cstrike\maps
Replacing the C:\ with your drive letter and "user-name" with your steam login.

==============
Removal:
==============
Remove all copied files.
